*Nedelja* je obično veoma lepa i sunčana. (Sunday is usually very nice and sunny.)

U *nedelji* odmori se i uživaj. (On Sunday, rest and enjoy yourself.)

U *nedelju* se obično idemo na ručak kod bake. (On Sunday, we usually go to grandma's for lunch.)

*Nedeljom* se obično provodi vreme sa porodicom. (Usually, Sunday is spent with family.)

*Nedelja* je najlepši dan sedmice. (Sunday is the best day of the week.)